show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/4fDnpv
show.description: The Wife Behind the Empire tells the story of Janvi, a woman betrayed by her husband Veer and his family, who try to replace her with his ex, Soniya. But when Janvi reveals her hidden strength and true identity as the CEO of Acme Group, she shocks everyone, turning her heartbreak into power and reclaiming control over her life and destiny.
